query getConfiguration($language: String!) {
  configuration(localeFilters: {locale: $language}) {
    parkIsOpen
    parkOpeningTime
    parkClosingTime
    parkText
    parkInfoBanner
    parkLatitude
    parkLongitude
    parkRadiusMeters
    welcomeImage
    mapColorShow
    mapColorRestaurant
    minimumVersionIos
    minimumVersionAndroid
    cloudinaryProxyUrl
    enableMapDirections
    enableBillet
    enableFavoris
    __typename
  }
  locales {
    iso
    label
    __typename
  }
}

query getAttractions($language: String!) {
  openAttractions(localeFilters: {locale: $language}, orderBy: [{field: TITLE, order: ASC}]) {
    id
    drupalId
    title
    slug
    summary
    description
    experience {
      id
      drupalId
      label
      color
      __typename
    }
    mapId
    latitude
    longitude
    features {
      id
      label
      value
      icon
      __typename
    }
    headerV1
    thumbnailV1
    headerV2
    thumbnailV2
    sliders {
      picture
      order
      __typename
    }
    minAge
    order
    isNew
    isBest
    hasQueuingCut
    hasQueuingCutFear
    hasPicturePoint
    blocks
    labels
    __typename
  }
}
